## Events API

### Get All Events
GET http://localhost:5000/api/events

### Get All Events with Filters
GET http://localhost:5000/api/events?search=tech&sortBy=date&sortOrder=asc

### Get Event by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/events/1

### Create Event
POST http://localhost:5000/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "AI Conference 2025",
  "description": "Leading AI experts discussing the future of artificial intelligence",
  "location": "Silicon Valley, CA",
  "date": "2025-09-15T09:00:00Z",
  "totalSeats": 300,
  "price": 399.99,
  "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1485827404703-89b55fcc595e?w=800"
}

### Update Event
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/events/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Event Title",
  "price": 349.99,
  "availableSeats": 100
}

### Delete Event
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/events/1

